A simple Hazel loop (practical)

scan_field()          # what’s changing?
listen_signals()      # who/what has information?
choose_next_move()    # small, reversible step
assign_roles()        # use strengths
act()                 # move now
check_morale()        # keep cohesion
update_plan()         # iterate

Invariant: keep the group alive, cohesive, and moving.

